data.description: MLS# 272233 Seller is offering a $5000 BUYER CREDIT for this dream home in the prestigious Canyon Lakes Golf neighborhood of Kennewick! Located right down the street from the clubhouse and course, this beautiful 3 bedroom home offers a perfect blend of elegance and comfort. As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the welcoming ambiance of this meticulously maintained home. The main level boasts a spacious and bright living area, luxurious primary suite, 1/2 bath and laundry room. The kitchen is a chefs delight with modern appliances, marble countertops, ample counter space, generously sized pantry and a convenient breakfast bar. An adjacent dining area provides the perfect space for family meals or entertaining guests. Upstairs, you'll discover two generously sized bedrooms, full bath and an additional flex space...perfect for that home office space, play room or recreation room.But the real charm of this property lies in the outdoor living spaces. Step outside to a beautifully landscaped backyard that's ideal for gatherings and relaxation. A covered patio is perfect for al fresco dining, and a custom fire pit area features built in cement seating and beckons you to cozy up by the fire with friends and family. You will find an abundance of plants and trees surrounding the rock beds, and the entire yard is enclosed with wood fencing, ensuring privacy and security for you and your loved ones. Don't miss the opportunity to make this impeccable Kennewick residence your own. Call your favorite realtor and schedule a showing today!
